Germany Postpones Introduction of Truck Toll, Bild Reports

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-07-01T06:01:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/germany-postpones-introduction-of-truck-toll-bild-reports.html
Germany  has delayed the introduction
of a road toll for trucks,  Bild  reported, without saying where
it got the information.  The toll was to have been introduced by the middle of the
year, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christian Vits in Frankfurt at 
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  